<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">A convoy carrying <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="VOA20001112.2100.0095.mrg-E3" TYPE="IDENT">UN</COREF> Human Rights Commissioner Mary Robinson</COREF> through <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">the West Bank</COREF></COREF> has come under gunfire .
