Palestinian police said that militant Jewish settlers in <COREF ID="22" TYPE="IDENT">Hebron</COREF> had fired at <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">the convoy</COREF> in an Israeli - controlled part of <COREF ID="22" TYPE="IDENT">the town</COREF> .
